[
  {
    "text": "One of the concepts that comes up over and over again with prolific creative minds that I've interviewed for the Tim Ferriss Show or for the book Tools of Titans is creating empty space.",
    "uid": "e3156277b6231639",
    "source": "Big_Think - Tim_Ferriss_on_Mastery_-_Start_with_End_Game_and_Make_Space_for_Crea",
    "start": 0.0,
    "end": 16.51
  },
  {
    "text": "And one of the guest Josh Weitskin who never does any media. Can I curse on this?",
    "uid": "af7ef337a7514508",
    "source": "Big_Think - Tim_Ferriss_on_Mastery_-_Start_with_End_Game_and_Make_Space_for_Crea",
    "start": 16.51,
    "end": 23.51
  },
  {
    "text": "Yeah, he always texts me with profoundly laden SMSes because I'm the only one who can pull him out of his cave to do media.",
    "uid": "1c22bb4f3749effb",
    "source": "Big_Think - Tim_Ferriss_on_Mastery_-_Start_with_End_Game_and_Make_Space_for_Crea",
    "start": 23.51,
    "end": 31.51
  },
  {
    "text": "But he is best known perhaps as the chess prodigy and I'll explain why put that in air quotes besides how funny it looks on camera.",
    "uid": "7d5052c9d811b0ae",
    "source": "Big_Think - Tim_Ferriss_on_Mastery_-_Start_with_End_Game_and_Make_Space_for_Crea",
    "start": 31.51,
    "end": 40.51
  },
  {
    "text": "That form the basis or who form the basis for searching for Bobby Fisher, both the book and the movie.",
    "uid": "06f741896e3d9550",
    "source": "Big_Think - Tim_Ferriss_on_Mastery_-_Start_with_End_Game_and_Make_Space_for_Crea",
    "start": 40.51,
    "end": 48.51
  },
  {
    "text": "He was very well known chess player and continues to be an incredible chess player.",
    "uid": "1ac7da5d239143ae",
    "source": "Big_Think - Tim_Ferriss_on_Mastery_-_Start_with_End_Game_and_Make_Space_for_Crea",
    "start": 48.51,
    "end": 53.51
  },
  {
    "text": "But he has applied his learning framework to more than chess. So he was a World Champion in Tai Chi Push-Hands.",
    "uid": "d9cc89b38a646190",
    "source": "Big_Think - Tim_Ferriss_on_Mastery_-_Start_with_End_Game_and_Make_Space_for_Crea",
    "start": 53.51,
    "end": 59.51
  },
  {
    "text": "It's the first black belt in Brazilian Jitsu under the Fina. I'm probably the best of all time Marcelo Garcia who trains in New York City.",
    "uid": "5e7fd5194744de82",
    "source": "Big_Think - Tim_Ferriss_on_Mastery_-_Start_with_End_Game_and_Make_Space_for_Crea",
    "start": 59.51,
    "end": 67.51
  },
  {
    "text": "He's a nine-time World Champion, something like that.",
    "uid": "f7231763fbed399a",
    "source": "Big_Think - Tim_Ferriss_on_Mastery_-_Start_with_End_Game_and_Make_Space_for_Crea",
    "start": 67.51,
    "end": 70.51
  },
  {
    "text": "And he's now tackling paddle surfing and he could apply to just about anything. He works with some of the top financial minds in the world.",
    "uid": "98afe6c2c53a4ea0",
    "source": "Big_Think - Tim_Ferriss_on_Mastery_-_Start_with_End_Game_and_Make_Space_for_Crea",
    "start": 70.51,
    "end": 77.51
  },
  {
    "text": "He's a hedge fund manager and beyond. The best of the best, top one percent.",
    "uid": "4d66f376dc43927f",
    "source": "Big_Think - Tim_Ferriss_on_Mastery_-_Start_with_End_Game_and_Make_Space_for_Crea",
    "start": 77.51,
    "end": 81.51
  },
  {
    "text": "So why? What are the principles that he shares? One of them is creating empty space, cultivating empty space as a way of life.",
    "uid": "613e1b57da3419ea",
    "source": "Big_Think - Tim_Ferriss_on_Mastery_-_Start_with_End_Game_and_Make_Space_for_Crea",
    "start": 81.51,
    "end": 89.51
  },
  {
    "text": "And these are all tied together so much in another one.",
    "uid": "e55075dabfeb1056",
    "source": "Big_Think - Tim_Ferriss_on_Mastery_-_Start_with_End_Game_and_Make_Space_for_Crea",
    "start": 89.51,
    "end": 92.51
  },
  {
    "text": "Learning the macro from the micro.",
    "uid": "e9b76876d2341123",
    "source": "Big_Think - Tim_Ferriss_on_Mastery_-_Start_with_End_Game_and_Make_Space_for_Crea",
    "start": 92.51,
    "end": 95.51
  },
  {
    "text": "And then beginning with the end in mind. And these all work together.",
    "uid": "3dc9890dc95c496e",
    "source": "Big_Think - Tim_Ferriss_on_Mastery_-_Start_with_End_Game_and_Make_Space_for_Crea",
    "start": 95.51,
    "end": 100.51
  },
  {
    "text": "So I'll explain in fact the last two first.",
    "uid": "8a985a4514998025",
    "source": "Big_Think - Tim_Ferriss_on_Mastery_-_Start_with_End_Game_and_Make_Space_for_Crea",
    "start": 100.51,
    "end": 105.51
  },
  {
    "text": "Josh learned to play chess.",
    "uid": "84260253094c3f0a",
    "source": "Big_Think - Tim_Ferriss_on_Mastery_-_Start_with_End_Game_and_Make_Space_for_Crea",
    "start": 105.51,
    "end": 107.51
  },
  {
    "text": "I should say more accurately was coached by his first real coach in the opposite direction when compared to most training.",
    "uid": "ab250ae9c77529de",
    "source": "Big_Think - Tim_Ferriss_on_Mastery_-_Start_with_End_Game_and_Make_Space_for_Crea",
    "start": 107.51,
    "end": 117.51
  },
  {
    "text": "And most chess books he was taught in reverse. What does that mean?",
    "uid": "31c0e42a8c768f8a",
    "source": "Big_Think - Tim_Ferriss_on_Mastery_-_Start_with_End_Game_and_Make_Space_for_Crea",
    "start": 117.51,
    "end": 120.51
  },
  {
    "text": "He began with the end game and with very few pieces.",
    "uid": "d25ddb7c104ff4f6",
    "source": "Big_Think - Tim_Ferriss_on_Mastery_-_Start_with_End_Game_and_Make_Space_for_Crea",
    "start": 120.51,
    "end": 124.51
  },
  {
    "text": "So they cleared all the pieces off the board instead of starting with openings.",
    "uid": "2344d7c2de123342",
    "source": "Big_Think - Tim_Ferriss_on_Mastery_-_Start_with_End_Game_and_Make_Space_for_Crea",
    "start": 124.51,
    "end": 128.51
  },
  {
    "text": "Meaning what do you do first? The first five to ten moves.",
    "uid": "1f7ec7379edfca3b",
    "source": "Big_Think - Tim_Ferriss_on_Mastery_-_Start_with_End_Game_and_Make_Space_for_Crea",
    "start": 128.51,
    "end": 131.51
  },
  {
    "text": "Start with the end game with king and pawn versus king.",
    "uid": "6b3b1009de3c4ca7",
    "source": "Big_Think - Tim_Ferriss_on_Mastery_-_Start_with_End_Game_and_Make_Space_for_Crea",
    "start": 131.51,
    "end": 136.51
  },
  {
    "text": "What does this do? Well, this forces you to focus on principles like opposition, creating space,",
    "uid": "c2087c5b6cf757b3",
    "source": "Big_Think - Tim_Ferriss_on_Mastery_-_Start_with_End_Game_and_Make_Space_for_Crea",
    "start": 136.51,
    "end": 144.51
  },
  {
    "text": "Zugswon, which is a principle of forcing your opponent to do anything that will destroy their position or anything they can do.",
    "uid": "7638eef5566dad85",
    "source": "Big_Think - Tim_Ferriss_on_Mastery_-_Start_with_End_Game_and_Make_Space_for_Crea",
    "start": 144.51,
    "end": 153.51
  },
  {
    "text": "Well, worse in their position.",
    "uid": "e62dee644033b15d",
    "source": "Big_Think - Tim_Ferriss_on_Mastery_-_Start_with_End_Game_and_Make_Space_for_Crea",
    "start": 153.51,
    "end": 156.51
  },
  {
    "text": "And these types of principles that you learn when there's an empty board with a few pieces accomplish a few things.",
    "uid": "3b0d8d9d6b1d7d38",
    "source": "Big_Think - Tim_Ferriss_on_Mastery_-_Start_with_End_Game_and_Make_Space_for_Crea",
    "start": 156.51,
    "end": 163.51
  },
  {
    "text": "Number one, you are learning the macro.",
    "uid": "cd60e0f6864f6368",
    "source": "Big_Think - Tim_Ferriss_on_Mastery_-_Start_with_End_Game_and_Make_Space_for_Crea",
    "start": 163.51,
    "end": 166.51
  },
  {
    "text": "The principles that you can apply throughout the game of chess in almost any scenario.",
    "uid": "02eb87957d5d44ef",
    "source": "Big_Think - Tim_Ferriss_on_Mastery_-_Start_with_End_Game_and_Make_Space_for_Crea",
    "start": 166.51,
    "end": 172.51
  },
  {
    "text": "Through the micro. This end game situation.",
    "uid": "ff94bbf92793952f",
    "source": "Big_Think - Tim_Ferriss_on_Mastery_-_Start_with_End_Game_and_Make_Space_for_Crea",
    "start": 172.51,
    "end": 177.51
  },
  {
    "text": "And these principles are adaptable.",
    "uid": "1493505f2743d6fa",
    "source": "Big_Think - Tim_Ferriss_on_Mastery_-_Start_with_End_Game_and_Make_Space_for_Crea",
    "start": 177.51,
    "end": 181.51
  },
  {
    "text": "You become a machine that can Bob and weave with the circumstances very effectively.",
    "uid": "df967cdcc9768aa8",
    "source": "Big_Think - Tim_Ferriss_on_Mastery_-_Start_with_End_Game_and_Make_Space_for_Crea",
    "start": 181.51,
    "end": 186.51
  },
  {
    "text": "Compared to that as Josh would put it if you're memorizing the openings.",
    "uid": "8a0058fad295f02c",
    "source": "Big_Think - Tim_Ferriss_on_Mastery_-_Start_with_End_Game_and_Make_Space_for_Crea",
    "start": 186.51,
    "end": 190.51
  },
  {
    "text": "This might be like memorizing recipes if you're learning to cook.",
    "uid": "0eb9f9ee43a34498",
    "source": "Big_Think - Tim_Ferriss_on_Mastery_-_Start_with_End_Game_and_Make_Space_for_Crea",
    "start": 190.51,
    "end": 195.51
  },
  {
    "text": "You're effectively stealing the answers from the teacher's guidebook to a test.",
    "uid": "6b7b1de0df3fbcd6",
    "source": "Big_Think - Tim_Ferriss_on_Mastery_-_Start_with_End_Game_and_Make_Space_for_Crea",
    "start": 195.51,
    "end": 199.51
  },
  {
    "text": "And you'll be able to beat your friends for a while.",
    "uid": "df6dc7ae192a43af",
    "source": "Big_Think - Tim_Ferriss_on_Mastery_-_Start_with_End_Game_and_Make_Space_for_Crea",
    "start": 199.51,
    "end": 202.51
  },
  {
    "text": "And maybe even be considered a pretty decent chess player.",
    "uid": "f37fe22194502a09",
    "source": "Big_Think - Tim_Ferriss_on_Mastery_-_Start_with_End_Game_and_Make_Space_for_Crea",
    "start": 202.51,
    "end": 205.51
  },
  {
    "text": "But on a deep level, you don't understand the game.",
    "uid": "7ca280a960809957",
    "source": "Big_Think - Tim_Ferriss_on_Mastery_-_Start_with_End_Game_and_Make_Space_for_Crea",
    "start": 205.51,
    "end": 207.51
  },
  {
    "text": "And you'll never progress past that and you'll get beaten by really good players.",
    "uid": "7a7607703360fc4a",
    "source": "Big_Think - Tim_Ferriss_on_Mastery_-_Start_with_End_Game_and_Make_Space_for_Crea",
    "start": 207.51,
    "end": 212.51
  },
  {
    "text": "So that can be applied to, for instance, Brazilian Giucitsu, Josh told me,",
    "uid": "5ab448624baad95c",
    "source": "Big_Think - Tim_Ferriss_on_Mastery_-_Start_with_End_Game_and_Make_Space_for_Crea",
    "start": 212.51,
    "end": 217.51
  },
  {
    "text": "basically all of the most important principles of Giucitsu through one move at the end game, which is a choke called the guillotine,",
    "uid": "65476b5e564454c7",
    "source": "Big_Think - Tim_Ferriss_on_Mastery_-_Start_with_End_Game_and_Make_Space_for_Crea",
    "start": 217.51,
    "end": 226.51
  },
  {
    "text": "which Marcelo is famous for.",
    "uid": "1ccd443f6ec51f39",
    "source": "Big_Think - Tim_Ferriss_on_Mastery_-_Start_with_End_Game_and_Make_Space_for_Crea",
    "start": 226.51,
    "end": 228.51
  },
  {
    "text": "His version is called the Marcelo teen.",
    "uid": "0ecfdd458937e7e0",
    "source": "Big_Think - Tim_Ferriss_on_Mastery_-_Start_with_End_Game_and_Make_Space_for_Crea",
    "start": 228.51,
    "end": 230.51
  },
  {
    "text": "But it's effectively like this. You're choking.",
    "uid": "a8ddced7a27b9d03",
    "source": "Big_Think - Tim_Ferriss_on_Mastery_-_Start_with_End_Game_and_Make_Space_for_Crea",
    "start": 230.51,
    "end": 232.51
  },
  {
    "text": "Someone's heading here and he is a weird way of doing it.",
    "uid": "b911336c702d77ee",
    "source": "Big_Think - Tim_Ferriss_on_Mastery_-_Start_with_End_Game_and_Make_Space_for_Crea",
    "start": 232.51,
    "end": 234.51
  },
  {
    "text": "Where he puts his forearm on top of your shoulders.",
    "uid": "6ba38ae0ed117cb1",
    "source": "Big_Think - Tim_Ferriss_on_Mastery_-_Start_with_End_Game_and_Make_Space_for_Crea",
    "start": 234.51,
    "end": 236.51
  },
  {
    "text": "Pretty wicked. If you want to be put on conscious, you can go to that gym and experience that yourself.",
    "uid": "fd816f369f0cd944",
    "source": "Big_Think - Tim_Ferriss_on_Mastery_-_Start_with_End_Game_and_Make_Space_for_Crea",
    "start": 236.51,
    "end": 241.51
  },
  {
    "text": "But that can also be applied to many, many other things, for instance.",
    "uid": "bc17a3e7f5c258d7",
    "source": "Big_Think - Tim_Ferriss_on_Mastery_-_Start_with_End_Game_and_Make_Space_for_Crea",
    "start": 241.51,
    "end": 247.51
  },
  {
    "text": "If you're trying to build a startup.",
    "uid": "62eafb72a847b7c3",
    "source": "Big_Think - Tim_Ferriss_on_Mastery_-_Start_with_End_Game_and_Make_Space_for_Crea",
    "start": 247.51,
    "end": 249.51
  },
  {
    "text": "This is a common trendy thing to do these days.",
    "uid": "eeb9068d54a1b1bd",
    "source": "Big_Think - Tim_Ferriss_on_Mastery_-_Start_with_End_Game_and_Make_Space_for_Crea",
    "start": 249.51,
    "end": 253.51
  },
  {
    "text": "And I think everybody should start a business at some point.",
    "uid": "031fb36d086011c0",
    "source": "Big_Think - Tim_Ferriss_on_Mastery_-_Start_with_End_Game_and_Make_Space_for_Crea",
    "start": 253.51,
    "end": 256.51
  },
  {
    "text": "But in startup game, in say Silicon Valley, where I live,",
    "uid": "333b5c5c46a425c2",
    "source": "Big_Think - Tim_Ferriss_on_Mastery_-_Start_with_End_Game_and_Make_Space_for_Crea",
    "start": 256.51,
    "end": 260.51
  },
  {
    "text": "if you're going to go into the venture backed world.",
    "uid": "cf802a9e6eb6419c",
    "source": "Big_Think - Tim_Ferriss_on_Mastery_-_Start_with_End_Game_and_Make_Space_for_Crea",
    "start": 260.51,
    "end": 262.51
  },
  {
    "text": "Well, you and your founder better think a lot about the end game.",
    "uid": "c88468a54b789405",
    "source": "Big_Think - Tim_Ferriss_on_Mastery_-_Start_with_End_Game_and_Make_Space_for_Crea",
    "start": 262.51,
    "end": 265.51
  },
  {
    "text": "And you should definitely have an agreement, at least a working agreement,",
    "uid": "c66993b9702a386e",
    "source": "Big_Think - Tim_Ferriss_on_Mastery_-_Start_with_End_Game_and_Make_Space_for_Crea",
    "start": 265.51,
    "end": 270.51
  },
  {
    "text": "a tentative agreement, on what type of exit, say acquisition offer, is acceptable to you.",
    "uid": "a97a1b48dc6793b3",
    "source": "Big_Think - Tim_Ferriss_on_Mastery_-_Start_with_End_Game_and_Make_Space_for_Crea",
    "start": 270.51,
    "end": 275.51
  },
  {
    "text": "If those end goal components aren't in place.",
    "uid": "d5ff9fa13f9c8bb5",
    "source": "Big_Think - Tim_Ferriss_on_Mastery_-_Start_with_End_Game_and_Make_Space_for_Crea",
    "start": 275.51,
    "end": 281.51
  }
]